title: Air Fryer Beef Tips
directions: Preheat the Air Fryer at 400°F for 4 minutes.
Spread the steak, onions, peppers and mushrooms in even layer in air fryer basket. Air fry at 400°F for 10-18 minutes, shaking and flipping and the steak and mushrooms about 3 times
Check the steak to see how well done it is cooked. If you want the steak more done, add an extra 2-5 minutes of cooking time.
ingredients: 1 lb. steaks , cut into 1” cubes & patted dry
